UML:TaggedValue.value: Service providers or developers will upload AAL services.xml

Using web interface or ide plugin, authenticated service provider uploads a previously prepared service to the uStore, and then the system checks the correctness of all information. According to the metadata of the service and the properties of the service provider (he may be declared as trusted), the successfully checked service is published, or sent to an administrator for approval.
